data.description: Spacious, well maintained home with great curb appeal sits on a large 3/4 acre lot in the desirable neighborhood of Colonial Pines in North Ft Myers located just minutes to I-75. This nice home features lots of natural light, neutral colors, high ceilings, wood laminate and tile flooring.  No Carpet! Beautiful open kitchen features large breakfast bar with decorative lighting, dome ceiling, granite countertops, tile backsplash, stainless appliances and white cabinetry.  Private Master suite with big bathroom, decorative tile, walk in shower and oversized walk in closet. Two additional guest rooms both also w/walk in closets. Fourth bedroom has 1/2 bath and private entry door...perfect for a home office. Enjoy the SW Florida weather in your own free form pool w/domed screen enclosure, big covered lanai & pass thru window to kitchen. Two car garage with expansive driveway & plenty of parking for additional cars, boat or RV. Big fenced back yard has mature trees & lots of room for additional buildings.  No Deed Restrictions!  No HOA! Close to shopping and restaurants. Homes in this neighborhood don't come on the market often, make your showing appointment today before it is gone!
